content: I'm doing okay so far. I think I'm going to plan out my meals for the next few days and then make a shopping list based on what I need. I'm still trying to remember what I have at home, but I know I need to pick up some milk and a few other things. Oh, and I just remembered that I went to Walmart last Saturday and got a bunch of stuff, including some chicken breasts that I used to make chicken sandwiches yesterday.
